title: Dave Matthews Band - The Central Park Concert (2 Disc DVD)
description:
Dave Matthews Band - The Central Park Concert (2 Disc DVD)
Almost 3 hours of pure joy. 
The Best Dave Matthews Band live DVD released. Also feature apparence by Warren Haynes from Allmond Brothers Band. He plays for some 3 or 4 song and makes them go from great to unbelievable. 


Actors: Dave Matthews, Carter Beauford, Stefan Lessard, LeRoi Moore, Boyd Tinsley
Directors: Lawrence Jordan (II)
Format: DVD-Video, Live, NTSC
Language: English
Region: Region 1 (U.S. and Canada only)
Aspect Ratio: 1.78:1
Number of discs: 2
Studio: RCA
DVD Release Date: November 18, 2003
Run Time: 169 minutes
